name: 2024 The 6th World Symposium on Software Engineering
content: Publication and Indexing: All the papers will be peer reviewed by experts. The review result comes out in 15 to 20 days. Accepted, registered and presented papers will be published in the ACM Conference Proceedings, which will be indexed by Ei Compendex, Scopus, ISTP/CPCI and other academical databases. WSSE conference proceedings have been successfuly indexed by Scopus and EI since 2019 within three months after the online.
